column4:
Hello!
Welcome to the Level editor,
this is the best place
 to make your own playable levels.
 Hours of fun
The level editor\nuses the mouse to navigate arond,\nwith a drag on the middle click to pan.

Moving platforms are created by clicking
where the top left point should be,
 then where the bottom right should be.
 Then finally the final x position
 of where the platform should stop
 it's movement.
You can find grass,\n trees and rocks in the scenary\n section of the drop down list.
